ContentDesc_Deltametrie 3.0: Taken by curiosity, you activate something called the Savage Initiative at a Garlond Ironworks terminal. Apparently a program to address work-related stress, you are treated to a soothing song composed by a certain minstrel, its lush strains massaging your mind and adding vibrant flourishes to the memories of your trials within the Deltascape...
Instancecontenttextdata_17701_Text: There is no escape. You shall be a pawn in my grand games unto death.
Instancecontenttextdata_17704_Text: That concludes the first round. Let the board be changed!
Instancecontenttextdata_17705_Text: You've done well to survive the second round. But how will you fare in the next?
Instancecontenttextdata_17706_Text: Well, well, aren't you durable? But it's only a matter of time before you crumble.
Instancecontenttextdata_17707_Text: Four rounds over yet you still stand!? You clearly want for a challenge, and I shall give it to you!
Instancecontenttextdata_17717_Text: My dance holds all in its thrall!
Instancecontenttextdata_17718_Text: Let us add a special touch to the board. Oh, there's naught to fear...as long as you obey the rules.
Instancecontenttextdata_17719_Text: Yes, you need but abide by the symbols. A simple game, yes?
Instancecontenttextdata_17720_Text: How can you not grasp such a simple game? Are you failing on purpose?
Instancecontenttextdata_17721_Text: Mayhap that was too easy. But benevolent as I am, I shall grant you a prize nonetheless.
Instancecontenttextdata_17722_Text: Now then, let us increase the challenge with a delightful picture game!
Instancecontenttextdata_17723_Text: What's the matter? If you do not abide by the symbols, there will be a penalty.
Instancecontenttextdata_17724_Text: Come now, it really isn't all that hard. Surely you can do better.
